value.value: Mayo-Portland Adaptability Inventory-4 (MPAI-4) Sensitivity to mild symptoms: Focusing on thinking, physical or emotional problems attributed to brain injury; rate only how concern or worry about these symptoms affects current functioning over and above the effects of the symptoms themselves.

Mayo-Portland Adaptability Inventory-4 (MPAI-4) Initiation: Problems getting started on activities without prompting.

Mayo-Portland Adaptability Inventory-4 (MPAI-4) Transportation.

Modifications to the physical environment that facilitate employment are not considered as support.
Mayo-Portland Adaptability Inventory-4 (MPAI-4) Primary social role when paid employment is not primary desired social role.
